title: Ancient Memorial
review: Dakhini darwaza of Taj Agra is a memorial of Ancient Agra. It is located in Mohalla Tajganj. The mugal subedars constructed four gates – Bareilly darwaza, Hussaini darwaza, Jahanabadi darwaza and Dakhini darwaza.

title: Significant Darwaza
review: One of the 4 darwaza's, Dakhini is very popular with the locals and this is the first thing I visited right after getting down from the Agra railway station. You need to catch hold of  a local (esp. an oldie) to know its significance.

review: This is one of tourist attractions in agra. it has its own historic importance.

title: Dakhini
